 BNE ComputeXYOnTile<br /><br />&nbsp; ;Verify the collision with the left part of the brick<br />PerformBallColWithBrickLeft:<br />&nbsp; LDX BALL_POS_X_ON_TILE<br />&nbsp; LDA $0400, x<br />&nbsp; CMP #$2D<br />&nbsp; BEQ PerformBallCollisionWithBrick<br /></div>

		

